Louis Mann https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Louis_Mann 0 Louis Mann (20 April 1865 – 15 February 1931) was an American theatre actor and sometime director, who in his later life made a few appearances in motion pictures. He was married to actress and playwright Clara Lipman.
